/**
 * PhaseRequirementsSeeder — FLOW-37 Phase A bootstrap
 *
 * Manual bootstrap only (per bootstrap-boundary contract).
 * Phase A creates the components that cannot be generated by a flow topology
 * because they are prerequisites for flow topologies to run at all.
 *
 * What it creates:
 *   1. Phase requirement documents in xiigen-phase-requirements
 *      (one per FLOW-37 phase: A through F)
 *   2. 5 FLOW_DESIGN RAG seeds in xiigen-rag-patterns
 *      (teach future convergence runs about FLOW-37 design constraints)
 *
 * DNA-3: returns DataProcessResult<T>, never throws.
 * DNA-8: storeDocument before any emit.
 * DNA-5: tenantId from ALS — not passed to fabric methods.
 */

